6ffb6d3d-b89f-4e20-af94-7ca1424f1e4f.title: Tracker gnome 2
6ffb6d3d-b89f-4e20-af94-7ca1424f1e4f.text:
I can't talk now. If the guards catch me I'll be dead
gnome meat.

dfda0d83-1302-4e77-a7d5-96bfe52e5fec.title: <player>
dfda0d83-1302-4e77-a7d5-96bfe52e5fec.text:
The battle is far from over. If you have a pure heart
you will help us win.

f14e3686-8a72-41da-b9ee-e6727fcedad9.title: Tracker gnome 2
f14e3686-8a72-41da-b9ee-e6727fcedad9.text:
They caught me spying on the stronghold. They beat
and tortured me.

f03d9bd5-2cc7-40b6-8884-fece170c7625.title: Tracker gnome 2
f03d9bd5-2cc7-40b6-8884-fece170c7625.text:
But I didn't crack. I told them nothing. They can't
break me!

485b8492-c3f4-4ffe-92b0-855a769bff34.title: Tracker gnome 2
485b8492-c3f4-4ffe-92b0-855a769bff34.text: Don't be. I have the position of the stronghold!

23bc4796-60e3-437d-bf59-381806bbf4a7.text: The gnome tells you the y coordinate.

60b597fa-3f48-4c01-950d-6c6c0c340d1e.title: Tracker gnome 2
60b597fa-3f48-4c01-950d-6c6c0c340d1e.text: Now leave before they find you and all is lost.

f56cf314-519b-4fe3-ae81-bcdea9b99176.title: Tracker gnome 2
f56cf314-519b-4fe3-ae81-bcdea9b99176.text:
Well done, you've broken down their defences. This
battle must be ours.

fd9a8489-6556-40f0-840f-840aa6dfd749.title: Tracker gnome 2
fd9a8489-6556-40f0-840f-840aa6dfd749.text:
Now we have the orb I'm much better. Soon my
comrades will come and free me.

6509b1cd-e440-46f6-8a4f-fe1aa6df7a31.title: Tracker gnome 2
6509b1cd-e440-46f6-8a4f-fe1aa6df7a31.text:
When will this battle end? I feel like I've been locked up
my whole life.
